DESCRIPTION
"This is a modified copy of the original model definition file."
"The original observables and errors have been removed."
"New, realistically drawn observables are defined in the data definition files."

"Original project:	Lucarelli_CellSystems2017"
"RS project name:	Lucarelli_RS19"
"Random seed:		0002119000."

"Original description:"

"by Philippe Lucarelli"
"complex vs stats comparison"
"Complex_Formation_ppSmad new data added from martin and all the datasets to 100%"
"only 2 koff rates"
"MS ratios"
"Parameters to remove single complexes"
"Gene expression"

"model reduction after model selection"

"S2S4S4, ppS2ppS2ppS3, ppS2S4S4 and ppS2ppS3S4 necessary to describe all the data"


